*gdbm-1.8.3-r1 (01 Aug 2004)

  01 Aug 2004; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> +gdbm-1.8.3-r1.ebuild:
  Dont copy over the old library if it is of size 0 bytes; force those unlucky
  users to revdep-rebuild.

